{"word":"πρόσχημα","slug":"πρόσχημα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n90371\" key=\"pro/sxhma\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">πρόσχημα</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ατος</itype>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τό</gen>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">προέχω</etym>) <sense id=\"n90371.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">that which is held before</tr_>: hence, </sense> <sense n=\"I\" id=\"n90371.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">that which is held before to cover, screen, cloak</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὸ σῶφρον τοῦ ἀνάνδρου π</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:82\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.82</biblScope> </bibl>; <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">pretence, pretext</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πατὴρ . . σοὶ π. ἀεί, ὡς ἐξ ἐμοῦ τέθνηκεν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg005.perseus-grc1:525\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ El.\">El.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">525</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τοῦτο π. ποιούμενος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0540.tlg006.perseus-grc1:37\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lys.\">Lys.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.37</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; also <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">π. τοῦ λόγου</foreign> in the same sense, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greek